00076   //template< class align_T_iterator > my_float_t 
00077   my_float_t
00078   score(const ModelSitemap &model, const DbaseSitemap& dbase, 
00079         rigid_align_t *scores)
00080         //align_T_iterator scores)
00081   {
00082     WeightedSumsScore::score(model, dbase, scores);
00083     //my_float_t pt_score = WeightedSumsScore::score(model, dbase, scores);
00084   
00085     std::vector<my_float_t> &terms = scores->terms;
00086     uint start_idx = terms.size();
00087     terms.resize(terms.size() + A_num_terms);
00088     std::fill(terms.end() - A_num_terms, terms.end(), 0.0);
00089   
00090     my_float_t &closest_polar_sum = terms[0];
00091     my_float_t &polar_mismatch_sum = terms[1];
00092     my_float_t &AA_DD_sum = terms[2];
00093     my_float_t &doneptor_sum = terms[3];
00094     my_float_t &phobic_count = terms[4];
00095     my_float_t &unsat_polar_count = terms[5]; 
00096   
00097     // Surface complementarity
00098     my_float_t &num_surf_pts = terms[start_idx];
00099     my_float_t &num_faces = terms[start_idx + 1];
00100     my_float_t &RMSE = terms[start_idx + 2];
00101     my_float_t &area = terms[start_idx + 3];
00102     my_float_t &RMS_norm_err = terms[start_idx + 4];
00103     my_float_t &max_q_pt_dist = terms[start_idx + 5];
00104   
00105     const geometry::TransformableTrimesh& model_surf = 
00106       model.binding_site_mesh_handle();
00107     const geometry::SimpleTrimeshTwo& dbase_surf = 
00108       dbase.binding_site_mesh_handle();
00109     A_max_surf_pt_dist = dbase.max_corr_surf_pt_dist();
00110     init_storage(model_surf);
00111 
00112 //    std::cout << "number of model surf verts: "  
00113 //              << model_surf.number_of_vertices() << "\n";
00114 //    std::cout << "number of dset surf verts: "  
00115 //              << dbase_surf.number_of_vertices() << "\n";
00116   
00117     dbase_surf.compare(model_surf.vertices_begin(), 
00118                        model_surf.number_of_vertices(), A_surf_closest_pts, 
00119                        A_dists, model_surf.normals_begin(), A_best_normals, 
00120                        A_norm_dists, A_max_surf_pt_dist);
00121     model_surf.compute_features(A_dists, A_max_surf_pt_dist, A_norm_dists, 
00122   //  model_surf.compute_features(A_dists, 1.5, A_norm_dists, 
00123                                 &num_surf_pts, &num_faces, &RMSE, &RMS_norm_err,
00124                                 &area, &max_q_pt_dist);
00125     if(scale_terms()){
00126       // The terms before start_idx were scaled in the base class
00127       std::vector<my_float_t>::const_iterator max_val =
00128         model.get_max_feature_vals().begin() + start_idx;
00129       std::vector<my_float_t>::iterator t = terms.begin() + start_idx;
00130       for( ; t < terms.end(); ++t, ++max_val) *t /= *max_val;
00131   
00132       return SCALED_CONSTANT_TERM + 
00133              SCALED_POLAR_SUM_W * closest_polar_sum + 
00134              SCALED_POLAR_MISMATCH_W * polar_mismatch_sum + 
00135              SCALED_DD_OR_AA_POLAR_SUM_W * AA_DD_sum +
00136              SCALED_DONEPTOR_POLAR_SUM_W * doneptor_sum +
00137              SCALED_HPHOBIC_COUNT_W * phobic_count + 
00138              SCALED_UNSAT_POLAR_W * unsat_polar_count +
00139              SCALED_SURFACE_RMSE_W * RMSE;
00140   
00141     }else{
00142       return CONSTANT_TERM + 
00143              POLAR_SUM_W * closest_polar_sum + 
00144              POLAR_MISMATCH_W * polar_mismatch_sum + 
00145              DD_OR_AA_POLAR_SUM_W * AA_DD_sum +
00146              DONEPTOR_POLAR_SUM_W * doneptor_sum +
00147              HPHOBIC_COUNT_W * phobic_count + 
00148              UNSAT_POLAR_W * unsat_polar_count +
00149              SURFACE_RMSE_W * RMSE;
00150     }
00151   }

00164   inline void
00165   init_storage(const geometry::TransformableTrimesh& model_surf)
00166   {
00167     const int N = model_surf.number_of_vertices();
00168     if(N <= A_max_num_verts) return;
00169   
00170     if(A_surf_closest_pts){
00171       delete[] (A_surf_closest_pts);
00172      A_surf_closest_pts = 0;
00173      A_dists = 0;
00174     }
00175   
00176     A_max_num_verts = N;
00177     A_surf_closest_pts = new my_float_t[8 * N];
00178     A_dists = &A_surf_closest_pts[3*N];
00179     A_best_normals = &A_surf_closest_pts[4*N];
00180     A_norm_dists = &A_surf_closest_pts[7*N];
00181   }
